If the input data consists of 80 base clusters and we provide a read structure of \"36T8B8S28T\" then, before being converted to SAM records those bases will be split into 4 reads where read one consists of 36 cycles of template, read two consists of 8 cycles of barcode, read three will be an 8 base read of skipped cycles and read four is another 28 cycle template read.
